               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18410705-name-742" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18410705-name-742" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410705-name-742" type="surname" value="UPTON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410705-name-742" type="given" value="SOPHIA"></interp>SOPHIA UPTON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am servant to James Allett Leigh, of Upper Ken<lb></lb>nington Green. These three spoons are my master's—I placed them on a waiter on a chest of drawers, near the kitchen window, about eleven or twelve o'clock, on the 30th of June—I was away for a short time—when I came back the window was open, and these spoons were gone.</p>
               <p>
